Package: leafwax
Title: Bayesian Inversion of Leaf Wax d2H to Precipitation d2H
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Alex", "Bradley", , "abradley@wustl.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4044-2802"))
Description: Bayesian inversion of leaf wax hydrogen isotopes to reconstruct
    precipitation isotopes using hierarchical spatial models. Provides multiple
    Bayesian models with varying complexity and spatial interpolation using
    Gaussian processes. Models are pre-computed using Stan and stored as
    posterior distributions for fast prediction without requiring Stan installation.
